<% content_for :title, "Teacher Teacherへようこそ！" %>

<div class="p-4">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-6 text-gray-800">
    Teacher Teacherの<br>Discordサーバへご招待
  </h2>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 mb-6">
    <p class="text-blue-800">
      <strong><%= @invitation.invitee_name %></strong> さん、ようこそ！<br>
      あなたを <strong><%= @invitation.role.name %></strong> としてTeacher TeacherのDiscordコミュニティにご招待いたします。
    </p>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">📋 招待の手順</h3>

  <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
    <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-3">1</span>
      <span>Discordアカウントの準備</span>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-3">2</span>
      <span>Discordアカウントで認証</span>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-3">3</span>
      <span>サーバーへの参加完了</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 mb-6">
    <p class="text-yellow-800 text-sm">
      <strong>💡 ヒント:</strong> このプロセスは数分で完了します。もしDiscordが初めての方でも、順を追って案内しますのでご安心ください。
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center">
    <%= link_to "操作を進める", "/step1?code=#{@code}", class: "inline-block w-full bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition duration-300" %>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
      招待コード: <span class="font-mono bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded"><%= @code %></span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
